function.arguments:
{
  "message": "PubMed Agent, please search for peer-reviewed articles that discuss the mechanism by which Bridge Therapy—commonly low-dose corticosteroids—reduces inflammation in rheumatoid arthritis, specifically examining the downstream effect on CRP levels, monocyte activation, and fibroblast-like synoviocytes. We seek mechanistic studies and clinical trials describing how short-term Bridge Therapy influences pro-inflammatory cytokine signaling and matrix metalloproteinase activity in RA joints."
}

